{"tid":1834994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「國際線」民間不叫武漢肺炎，叫「中國肺炎」/「中國式肺炎」","createTime":"2020-01-22T15:55:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T15:58:50.000Z","uid":195252,"like":77,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"0f858cc5f1d897b785c982a4bec0233608fc0dc0","tid":1834994,"uid":195252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T15:55:21.000Z","msg":"首先，我好認同將今次的傳染病事件，提升為政治事件；中國每一次的天災，背後總離不開人禍，今次其實就係大陸人唔聽勸告，繼續賣野味，食野味，最後出現「武漢肺炎」傳播世界，輸出世界。<br />\n<br />\n為了要讓國際了解中國的邪惡，中國人的低智，而且好多外國人都唔知武漢係中國地方，我地係唔係應該將「武漢肺炎」，民間正名俗稱為「中國肺炎」，或者「中國式肺炎」，英文「Chinese pneumonia」，突顯背後人禍的荒謬？<br />\n<br />\n認同與否，大家討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c598735c364ed8218c6b77f0bfbb231f03600295","tid":1834994,"uid":195252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T15:55:59.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"5b3566a9e973c748d16640980e30c0da2ed84004","tid":1834994,"uid":35087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T15:56:38.000Z","msg":"Chinese Pneumonia"},{"pid":"38c96451f4be3e56347f80533c62944298b66b51","tid":1834994,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T15:59:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"278a5300cfe71d2668b7057ebb113d703d80fb6e","tid":1834994,"uid":9566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:00:04.000Z","msg":"Chinese Pneumonia"},{"pid":"3fafae778d329d07c4570e00dad237dc9042270d","tid":1834994,"uid":195252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:05:25.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"942c68f9556391204f783a1e42a1c4a17137dbcc","tid":1834994,"uid":66949,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:08:09.000Z","msg":"你而家係咪武獨?<br />\n武咩漢? 大家記住叫中國武漢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e49a76f4bc08dc3ed74f7a6d725dc17c8b25c86","tid":1834994,"uid":78304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:08:54.000Z","msg":"中国武漢肺炎"